{
  "stem": "2074.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's one thing I want you to know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You'll never know from anybody else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Jews had to undress themselves, completely nothing, before they lie in the grave.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Put the clothes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then they made announcement.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anybody who wants to come to get Jewish clothes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First, they search them if there's anything hidden, and then come get the clothes.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Manka ?] got a lot of these Jewish clothes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they wouldn't wear them the way they were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The size wasn't good or whatever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So while I was sitting there, I had some work to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So evidently, at least I paid for them my food or whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But she was a good friend besides because in the beginning, the biggest danger was they scared all the other nationalities.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you give a Jew a piece of bread, you go in the same grave with the Jew.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "See?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So but she was hiding me, and her father a Nazi.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she was not as much afraid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, did she have a husband that was aware of this?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] was her husband.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] was her husband--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and she had the daughter, the daughter [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sonia. ?] And then now when we went, she had another daughter.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Tania ?] was born after the war, with the husband and two daughters.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we stayed with them the whole couple of weeks at their house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my son had such a good time with them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were so nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were treating us royally.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my son brought them a big bundle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He gave them a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Gave [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Manka ?] money.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Sonia ?] got money, and [INAUDIBLE] got money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They all-- we gave them whatever-- whatever we could, very nice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
